    {
      "id": "1914750c-f3ba-80b9-82ea-c816decbf43b",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Paper discusses the implementation of resource recommender systems. Algorithm explores the algorithms and techniques used in recommender systems with a specific emphasis between personalization and privacy. Paper finishes with a discussion of implications of deploying this type of recommenders. ",
